4.kvt:
Koq loq naq nal goel neq khal heel nail nal goel dai
Aq meeq meeq dai heeq kivq nail loq nail ngaol.

5.kvt: Niaoq lal khi el-ail nia nail ganl.

10.kvt:
Naoq nail lavq khoel bhai aq duq niil
juq nee aol-Ail nia nail ngaol.

13.kvt:
Ul lul niil jiav khal ail haq neq nal
goel mao dai el-ail nia nail ngaol.

15.kvt:
Liq cav khaiq nail bhai jaol nail bhaq da nee nal
goel aq ma bhoel leevq nail nee bhuq-ail lao ail
nail  ngaol.

19.kvt: Al heel ngel-i mail tsaol-aq teevq gaq civq nieivq tsiq  nail hal tsiq tsiq nail coevq sil nail niil juq bhai moel lal haq  neq, pul-nvq khe gevq-ai thaq nail khe-ai ya nl nail ngaol.

20.kvt:
Aq yu juq bhai moeq bhaoq-ai pavq cuvq nail(Mask)
bivq yaoq. Al moeq bhaoq bhai pavq cuvq nail yuq nail
bhaq da nee aq yu juq mail hal tsiq tsiq nail civq nieivq
tsiq nail al juq yu bhai maq niaoq-ail nia-ail.

22.kvt:
Geeq laoq eeq naol
(Nal eel dov nail juq)

24.kvt: Aivq maq coevq sil gaoq neq, aiqv bhai aivq maq bhi niaoq lal dai yaol phaol nail gail pevq nia nail ngaol.

25.kvt: Nal goel niaoq lal khi ngaol-aoq nal goel nail se khi se laq maq dov lal dai jiav nia nail ngaol. Al hai ngaol-aoq neq nal goel neq niaoq lai nia nail ngaol.

26.kvt:
Khaq sil gaq bhai nal goel niaoq nail dai maq
heeq kivq Nail ngel-I mail ge gal laq-u bhai
tsoal-aq bhoi nail aq duq bhai yaol phaol yaoq.

29.kvt: Yaq thal/laoq liq nail aq lavq nioi thaiq duq

30.kvt: Cav nail thaoq joe khe thoiq nail nl maoq

31.kvt: Moeq bhao siv nail gal lal

33.kvt: Cav nail nl maoq teevq phaq ga nav

34.kvt: Moeq bhao-ai pavq cuvq nail nil maoq(mask) nail lavq niil phao khe

koq-nq piq-uq taq khe

37.kvt: Haoq gaqv gevq nail dail kheq

39.kvt: Aq yu juq nail aq lavq

40.kvt: Al uq tavq coevq sil nail juq nail thaiq khaq neq teevq povq ga nav yal kav lov kav bhai gail niaoq nia nail ngaol. Daoq ma uq huq daoq_

41.kvt: Nul juq iq sanl mail coevq sill al nia khi nal goel niaoq lal nia nail ngaol.

42.kvt:
Naol gaiq-a nail gaq nail maiv phaoq bhai aq-eel lav yao
haq neq

43.kvt: Maiv neev bhai aq-eel gaiq yaoq lai haq neq

44.kvt:
Ge gal lavq-u bhai nl maoq thoil juq teevq phaq ga nav
 Bhai naol nioi thaiq khi naoq nail maiv phaoq bhai gaoq
bhi yao lai haq neq

45.kvt:
Thoil thai deeq teev yaol phaol nail gal duq neq aq lavq
 bhai sav bhaiq-aq mail maq ngel haq kaoq haol kheq nail
ul lul mail aq meeq meeq dai ya tsiq nail ngaol.

46.kvt: Nal goel aq ma niil neq nl maoq yal kav nail kov tavq bhai Naq li mao dai lavq aq doevq doevq khi jaol niia nail ngaol.

49.kvt: Nal goel maq bhiq niaoq lal dai iq moeq ya laiq-nq gai Nail (5) phaq

50.kvt: Niil juq bhai tsao the haq neq mail ma-ail meeq nail ngaol.

51.kvt: Niai kev dai sav bhaiq-aq mail tsiq yaoq

54.kvt:
Naoq nail maiv phaoq bhai thaq lav yaoq (maq ngel haq)
yu nail maiv phaoq bhai gail thaq lav yao. Lav yao nail loq
lal haq neq iq moeq il moeq sav bhaiq-aq mail aq lavq aq
meeq meeq dai tsiq yaoq.

55.kvt: Hail pil bhal deil daoq sel nvq pov gul gaq dan-u kev dai  tsiq yaoq

59.kvt: Lavq pav kov tavq bhai tsiq yaoq

60.kvt: Maq doi maq doi dai ge nail neq khal heel bhai ge movq Nail.

61.kvt:
Ya lav yao khi mail ngaol-aoq thaq noeq haq naoq nail aq lavq bhai sav bhaiq-aq mail aq meeq meeq dai gaoq
 tsiq yaoq.

62.kvt: Moeq bhaoq-ai pavq cuvq nail lavq niil phao gail maq ya  lav-ail.

64.kvt:
Moeq bhaoq-ai pavq cuvq nail teevq laiq bhai mao dai
yuq moq ha neq nal goel aq ma neq a bhai gaoq doevq lal
nail ngaol.

65.kvt:
Moeq bhaoq-ai pavq cuvq nail(mask)teevq laiq neq
 teevq-n maq ngel nail neq thaq yuq. Aq nuq nuq-ail haq
liv ha pivq yaoq.

66.kvt: Jal tsoiq bhai cav khuq-i mail khuq khi yuq yaoq.

70.kvt:
Yaoq gaq yaoq-ao nee yovq ga yovq gaq nail aq lavq siv
 nail phal khail yuq yaoq.

71.kvt:
Jaq jaq daol daol/ miq jaq khaol tsil khe yuq nail nl maoq
Ul cuvq khaoq-aq-nq/ aq lavq siv nail phal khail niil juq
bhai Teevq gaq khe-ai thaq yuq.

72.kvt: Naoq nail lavq ceevq-i mail maiv phaoq bhai khal hai khi mail ngaol-aoq maq lav yao kivq-ail.

73.kvt: Lol gov laol phao-u bhai lavq ceevq maq ngel haq bavq  Puv-i mail thaoq phao yaoq. Pevq lai kivq ha neq aq lavq-i  mail thaq phao.

75.kvt:
Lavq niil nee mail kovq
lal nail aq yanq.

76.kvt:
Jaq jaq daol daol maq jaq
maq daol nail gaiq laq bhai

77.kvt: Aq lavq bhai sav bhaiq-aq-i mail khaq mao gail tsiq yaoq.

80.kvt:
Tsaol-aq yaq yaoq gaq yaoq-ao
nee mail ya cov ya lav-ail nail
phaq nee jel-ail heeq phaq-ail
jaol yaoq.

81.kvt: Tsaol-aq yaq yaoq gaq yaoq-ao nee mail ya cov ya lav-ail nail phaq nee jel-ail heeq phaq-ail jaol yaoq.
